class Solution {
    /**
    You rae givne a word. Your task is to find the lcosest ovwel that stands between
    two consonants from the right side of the word (case sensiitve).

    Voewsl in the beginning and ending dosen't count. Return empty string if yuo didn't
    find any voewl met the above condition.

